30:50.849 --> 30:52.067
Might be yours.

30:52.111 --> 30:54.635
I am a big fan.
I love your game.

30:54.678 --> 30:56.419
- You know who that is?
- Big Baby?

30:56.463 --> 30:59.118
You know who Glen Davis is, right?

30:59.161 --> 31:00.293
Correct.

