31:23.664 --> 31:25.057
Oh, of course.

31:26.580 --> 31:29.931
Oh, yes, yes. Pop that booty.
Pop that booty. Pop.

31:36.982 --> 31:38.679
- Whitney.
- Nice to meet you.

31:38.722 --> 31:39.898
Nice to meet you.

31:39.941 --> 31:41.551
Did you put shimmer
on your ta-tas?

31:41.595 --> 31:44.293
- I did.
- They look good.

31:44.337 --> 31:46.339
I got a little shimmer going.

31:46.382 --> 31:48.080
Thanks for having this
for Sharrieff. It's amazing.

31:48.123 --> 31:49.646
It's so...

31:49.690 --> 31:50.952
Oh!

31:50.996 --> 31:54.303
So we're this...

31:55.739 --> 31:59.047
It's a good night,
and I'm just saying, like,

31:59.091 --> 32:00.701
I met with Lisa.

32:02.833 --> 32:04.400
And I haven't had the chance
to talk to you about it,

32:04.444 --> 32:06.837
and, like, I don't wanna
burden tonight with it.

32:06.881 --> 32:10.972
But the fact that you're here
is to me, like, maturity.

32:11.016 --> 32:13.018
I don't think it's a big deal.

32:13.061 --> 32:15.237
I think it's a huge deal.

32:15.281 --> 32:16.717
