and crying

32:16.760 --> 32:18.197
in the corner at home,
it's not me.

32:18.240 --> 32:20.503
I didn't do anything wrong.

32:20.547 --> 32:22.853
I love that Meredith
is a woman of principle,

32:22.897 --> 32:24.812
but on that same note, there's
a Mormon proverb that says,

32:24.855 --> 32:28.511
"Where much is given,
much is expected."

32:28.555 --> 32:30.818
So if you've given 10 years
to a friendship,

32:30.861 --> 32:32.646
you're expected to have
a conversation

32:32.689 --> 32:35.954
about a path to forgiveness.

32:35.997 --> 32:38.130
It is brave of you
to be here tonight.

32:38.173 --> 32:39.435
